Classical Swine Fever - Russia
--------------------------
Information received on [and dated] Thu 13 Feb 2020 from Dr Nikolay Vlasov, deputy head, Federal Service for Veterinary and Phytosanitary Surveillance, Ministry of Agriculture, Moscou, Russia

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 6 Feb 2020
Date of confirmation of the event: 11 Feb 2020
Report date: 13 Feb 2020
Date submitted to OIE: 13 Feb 2020
Reason for notification: recurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 11 Jul 2019
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: classical swine fever virus
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country.

New outbreaks (1)
