Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: unknown or inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: surveillance within containment and/or protection zone; screening; official disposal of carcasses, by-products, and waste; control of wildlife reservoirs; disinfection; vaccination permitted (if a vaccine exists); no treatment of affected animals
